Title: Hell
Plot: Ted, Dougal and Jack go on an all-expenses-spared holiday to Kilkelly Caravan Park. They meet a young couple, and are soon in trouble with the police. Entertainment comes in the shape of St Kevin's Stump and the Magic Road. Father Jack goes missing; Father Noel Furlong and his youth group turn up to put the final nail in the coffin of the holiday.
GuestStars: Tony Guilfoyle, Graham Norton, Pat Shortt, Liam Hayden, Anne Hayden, Stephen Gallagher (III), Tom Farrelly, Yvonne Shanley, Sharon Carroll, Robert English, Joe Taylor, Laura Bermingham, Gerry O'Brien, Ben Keaton
